#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "<color_light_blue>BL9-175%-monster-resilience-version</color>"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for <color_light_blue>BL9-175%-monster-resilience-
#. version</color>
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"\n"
"<color_yellow>Gigantic sci-fi action adventure expansion mod </color>\n"
" <color_yellow>PLEASE, SET 'Monster evolution scaling factor' DURING IN-GAME WORLD GENERATION AROUND 5.00 FOR PROPER GAMEPLAY EXPERIENCE </color>\n"
"\n"
" <color_light_cyan> Huge exotic locations - The Safety Base Central Hub with missions, Mad Cult's Tainted Medieval Castle, Huge Abandoned Industrial Facility, Secret Tyrannical Organization's Militarized Island, Lush and Mysterious Fortified Biomes, Mobile Military Base of Aliens (custom huge structures!)</color>,<color_red> vile and horribly mutated dangerous monsters, cultists, mutants, aliens, aliens, military, advanced military aliens</color>\n"
" <color_light_blue> New custom modern and hi-tech weapons along with armor of different tiers. Stranger Trader complex trading system with lots of goods. Simple, but handy crafting system to craft ammo, weapons. Tiers of artifacts (a lot of them!) that buff skills, stats. Deep lore system in a form of journals, dialogues, speeches. Safe hub area with a very helpful Android with missions </color>\n"
" <color_light_blue> Adds locations, items, monsters, recipes, NPCs with lore inspired by iconic Resident Evil series made by Capcom along with Half Life series made by Valve as well</color>"
msgstr ""

