"my masters, as we have all, hoped for, thanks to your work! If inhabitants "
"decide to go outside, shield will be deactivated for a split second then "
"turned on again. If inhabitants decide to go back here, scanners, installed "
"near entrance, will scan them, if they are former inhabitants, inhabitants "
"will be able to go back here, shield will be deactivated for split second "
"then turned back on again. My masters ordered me to advise you to make this "
"your permanent, safe home here. Make a family, bring your love here, have "
"children, adopt children, live as a civilization hopefully as well"
msgstr ""

